Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Fears over US deficit
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b0441r19
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 27 Nov 1988
The economy will be the first challenge facing the new president when his term starts in January. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less